sentences: Ryan Shore (born 29 December 1974) is a Canadian composer, songwriter, conductor, music producer, and music director for film, television, virtual reality, records, games, concerts, and theater.

He is currently scoring the upcoming Lin-Manuel Miranda movie musical In the Heights (additional music), The Not-Too-Late Show with Elmo (HBO Max), Mark Steven Johnson's romantic comedy feature Love, Guaranteed (Netflix), Star Wars Galaxy of Adventures (Lucasfilm), and score and songs for Go!
